[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 6.359,
    "text": "Thank you, I am Ken Jeong, or as Ellen pronounces it, Ken Je-young."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.36,
    "endTime": 13.25,
    "text": "Now it is an honor to be guest hosting for Ellen \"Degelenergenes\" (Deliberate mispronounciation of \"DeGeneres\")"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.25,
    "endTime": 17.81,
    "text": "So, but as you can see Ellen isn't here today."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.81,
    "endTime": 22.479999999999997,
    "text": "I want to tell you exactly what she's going through, but you know my movie, The Hangover?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.48,
    "endTime": 23.12,
    "text": "You know that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.39,
    "endTime": 27.437,
    "text": "Actually it's not that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.437,
    "endTime": 29.27,
    "text": "I just wanted to plug my movie The Hangover."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.27,
    "endTime": 32.03,
    "text": "So it's doing amazing on DVD."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.0,
    "endTime": 43.662,
    "text": "Ellen has the day off, so obviously I was asked to fill in because apparently she and I wear the same size suit."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.662,
    "endTime": 44.62,
    "text": "Actually you know what?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.62,
    "endTime": 47.94,
    "text": "My wife and kids are here today in the audience."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.94,
    "endTime": 49.129,
    "text": "Where are they?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.13,
    "endTime": 50.967000000000006,
    "text": "Want to give them a shout out?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.99,
    "endTime": 55.49,
    "text": "Hey!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.49,
    "endTime": 57.0,
    "text": "Look at them."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.0,
    "endTime": 60.0,
    "text": "Oh, wow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.0,
    "endTime": 63.75,
    "text": "Look at the frown on their faces, huh?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.36,
    "endTime": 67.25,
    "text": "All right, all right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.03,
    "endTime": 70.88,
    "text": "I didn't force her to be here at all."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.88,
    "endTime": 72.899,
    "text": "That is my wife, if you go back."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.9,
    "endTime": 74.30000000000001,
    "text": "That's my wife Tran."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.78,
    "endTime": 81.03,
    "text": "And that is the apple of my eye, Alexa."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.48,
    "endTime": 87.2,
    "text": "And what's your name, sweetie?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.2,
    "endTime": 87.8,
    "text": "I'm kidding."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.8,
    "endTime": 88.3,
    "text": "Zooey."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.3,
    "endTime": 88.84,
    "text": "Zooey."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.84,
    "endTime": 90.07000000000001,
    "text": "Don't get mad, don't get mad."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.07,
    "endTime": 93.22,
    "text": "All right, all right, all right, all right, all right,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.22,
    "endTime": 95.88,
    "text": "All right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.88,
    "endTime": 97.46,
    "text": "Don't worry, we're cutting all this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.0,
    "endTime": 103.91,
    "text": "I'll be honest, I brought them here because I'm a little nervous."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.91,
    "endTime": 108.77,
    "text": "This is actually my... it's actually my first time ever hosting a talk show, so thank you, Ellen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.77,
    "endTime": 110.497,
    "text": "This has been a huge honor."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.434,
    "endTime": 115.178,
    "text": "I've had an amazing time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.178,
    "endTime": 117.61,
    "text": "It's been incredible."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.61,
    "endTime": 122.58,
    "text": "I have never, ever done this before, so I just gotta... I just gotta reference what I know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.58,
    "endTime": 124.8,
    "text": "So I'm an actor."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.8,
    "endTime": 126.03,
    "text": "I'm a comedian."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.03,
    "endTime": 127.9,
    "text": "And this is true."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.9,
    "endTime": 129.044,
    "text": "I'm also a doctor."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.88,
    "endTime": 139.2,
    "text": "So just for me to make me feel comfortable, I need you all to disrobe."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.2,
    "endTime": 141.41,
    "text": "If that's okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.41,
    "endTime": 141.91,
    "text": "No?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.803,
    "endTime": 144.47,
    "text": "Yeah, it's true."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.47,
    "endTime": 148.24,
    "text": "I was a general practitioner and I worked full time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.24,
    "endTime": 151.72,
    "text": "Actually I would... any general practitioners in the crowd?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.72,
    "endTime": 152.22,
    "text": "Good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.22,
    "endTime": 154.42,
    "text": "Let's talk about them."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.42,
    "endTime": 157.839,
    "text": "General practitioners, we are the dumbest of all doctors."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.84,
    "endTime": 158.42000000000002,
    "text": "All right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.42,
    "endTime": 160.059,
    "text": "Like in general I knew nothing, okay?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.777,
    "endTime": 163.35899999999998,
    "text": "If a patient came up to me, say, doctor, what... what do I have?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.36,
    "endTime": 163.69000000000003,
    "text": "I don't know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.69,
    "endTime": 164.77,
    "text": "In general you're sick."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.77,
    "endTime": 166.57000000000002,
    "text": "I don't know these things."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.57,
    "endTime": 168.4,
    "text": "I'm going to refer you to a specificicst."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.0,
    "endTime": 175.01,
    "text": "My whole point is I love doing comedy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.01,
    "endTime": 181.25,
    "text": "I'm living out a dream, but honestly I miss my patients, and I miss helping people."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.25,
    "endTime": 190.792,
    "text": "So today, I thought I'd help all of you out with any medical questions you may have in my segment, Ask Dr. Ken."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.91,
    "endTime": 204.524,
    "text": "Those are my real abs."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.524,
    "endTime": 207.36,
    "text": "I had a sit-up coach."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.36,
    "endTime": 209.82000000000002,
    "text": "Where is Adrienne Lee?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.82,
    "endTime": 215.54999999999998,
    "text": "My question was, why do some Asians get Asian glow, and is it dangerous?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 215.55,
    "endTime": 220.8,
    "text": "Got it, why do some Asians get Asian glow, or like the Asian flush if you will."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 220.8,
    "endTime": 230.29000000000002,
    "text": "Like basically it is due to a lack of an enzyme called acetaldehyde dehydrogenase, which metabolizes alcohol in the body."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 230.29,
    "endTime": 238.019,
    "text": "And when you have an accumulation of said substance, you can get that Asian glow, or in American terms looks like a tomato."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 238.02,
    "endTime": 245.28,
    "text": "So it's... and but just to be clear, I can also answer non-Asian medical questions."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 245.28,
    "endTime": 247.24,
    "text": "I just wanted to throw that out there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 247.24,
    "endTime": 250.42000000000002,
    "text": "I don't want everyone to assume that's my only area of expertise."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 250.42,
    "endTime": 251.73,
    "text": "So you know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 251.73,
    "endTime": 252.81,
    "text": "I help out whites."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 255.15,
    "endTime": 257.97,
    "text": "Yup, yup. Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 257.97,
    "endTime": 259.86,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 259.86,
    "endTime": 261.53200000000004,
    "text": "Thank you, Adrienne."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 263.34,
    "endTime": 265.109,
    "text": "Keep it real, Adrienne."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 265.11,
    "endTime": 266.01,
    "text": "All right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 266.01,
    "endTime": 270.06,
    "text": "So where is Mafa?"
